<% if (isAngular) { %>### Angular / Web
- **Signals mandatory:** `signal()`, `computed()`, `effect()` ‚ÄĒ never `BehaviorSubject`
- **Injection:** always `inject()`, never constructor injection
- **HTTP:** always `RepoHttp` (not `HttpClient` directly)
- **Styles:** CSS theme variables (`--color-*`) ‚ÄĒ see `docs/frontend-ui-ux-guidelines.md`
- **No hardcoded Tailwind:** never `text-blue-500`, always `text-(--color-primary)`

<% } %><% if (isNestjs) { %>### NestJS / Backend
